text.tspan: 77.8% of 10 users said that they choose to look at New In
products before anything else. So for that reason, I made sure
that New products were easy to find and to easily transititon
from the dashboard through the purchasing user flow.
33.3% of users stated that the part that was most enjoyable about
popular e-commerce fashion sites was how easy it was for them to find
what they needed. For that reason, I removed any extra bells and whistles
I thought would be visisually appealing and focused on the UI being as
simple and easy as possible. Other responses included a fast
purchasing flow, website aesthetics, and visible FAQs and contact
88.9% of users stated that they trust a website even more if they were to receive a prompt
email confirmation for their transaction. From this I thought of creating a profile for the users
so that their information would be saved and when they log in or make any transaction, they
will recieve the email confirmation immidiatly with little effort.
